Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the infamous Sea of Fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that no one's gone inside and lived to tell the tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty famous story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, there's a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, halt engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, General Metalhead, show us what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of Hideauze approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They clearly have the edge in terms of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I hypothesize that their combat capabilities are inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest taking individual action.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I intended to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing for coordinated attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd save us some effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could keep this up forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earthian Hideauze appear to be significantly inferior to those previously encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Their combat capabilities are 1/120th of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With current armaments, continuing to repel them will pose no difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Comment: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Comment: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TS 0308}Deep Sea Secret{~dead sea scrolls}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Just maintain the course now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep an eye on the depth gauge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I do {\i1}not{\i0} wanna get lost in the middle of a bunch of whalesquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they can put curses on you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about if we just follow the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna screw up again.{Raze, please check: But the other people weren't really there or to be held responsible for what happened. I thought it was his way of saying that he wasn't going to mess up like he did with his brother.}{yeah, i was sorta going for a "watch us, brother, we aren't gonna screw up like the last time" kind of thing, but whatever you guys feel works best. changed to "I'm"}{Xythar, omakase}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.02,Default,,0,0,90,,Bro, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,90,,I've never seen so many whalesquids in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,90,,No need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,90,,We'll be fine as long as we don't provoke them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.41,Default,,0,0,90,,Let's go around and cut towards 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,90,,10 o'clock. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,90,,A real treasure island, just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,90,,Was something this awesome really built by humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep watch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, I'll be back before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are these stupidly huge machines all over the place.{+1}{just for you}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't some residential building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an industrial facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A whalesquid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is seriously incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,These aren't lousy parts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but true relics of the ancient civilization!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think it's about time to head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't pull up everything by ourselves anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I need to get an idea of the place for when we come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm opening the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this huge thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! This is a whalesquid—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: 23% of my total energy has been depleted from using Maximize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Its usage underwater is highly inefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought this melee weapon.{Xythar, if you could find a less awkward description of this weapon, I'd be eternally grateful. Otherwise, as is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the main force?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Activating proximity fuse. Launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So they really {\i1}can{\i0} be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like they aren't demons or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, how's it going down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, just lure them out of their nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be ready for them in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right ahead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: density of enemy units increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their numbers are too high to engage simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Recommending retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good up here! Anytime you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Activating anti-shock shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No damage. Deactivating shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, 67% of detected enemy forces have been annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Percentage increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done with that, move on to the next step of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep throwing them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough, but is that Yunboro gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That metalhead's really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason to hold back, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all those lightbugs! That blast of water was glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, fish can't survive here, but the whalesquids can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy forces appear to be retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that they have shifted to defense of their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Their base...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the nest Pinion mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Echolocation analysis complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Displaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: overall fatigue levels reaching dangerous levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Recommending retreat and a later assault at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm passing up this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Proceeding with current mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ion concentration rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ongoing electrolytic reaction detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful electromagnetic field discharge from inside the target confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Activating anti-shock shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Pinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you copy, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ledo! Metalhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had us worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's get a move on ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, they're much more vulnerable than they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that a lack of natural enemies has resulted in their devolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The analysis can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy remaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty-three percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo and the metalhead did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That treasure is as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, prepare to drop the anchors!{berth? dock?}{It didn't seem to me like they were docking, since that usually implies/connotes land. Also, "berth" is a really inaccessible word.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a thing! This fog is way too thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the cutie's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{with }Pinion being the one in charge and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They could at least report on their progress so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do now is put our faith in Pinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They appear to be fledgling Hideauze.{Xythar, how do you feel about "fledgling" before or after "Hideauze"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are... Hideauze children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Much is unknown regarding the Hideauze life cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is valuable information.{so he proceeds destroying them lol}{kill first, study later}{leaving this as is for the lulz}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these really Hideauze?{Raze, please check: addition of "small things" or "small organisms"}{i'd rather something unspecific since he doesn't actually mention that stuff and it's a pretty short line, which i think is the point. it's sort of like he's in a state of surprise/wonder and asks "Are these... Hideauze?"}{My only concern was that he ~just~ asked if these were Hideauze kids. So I was going for the "how can such kawaii things turn into those things I hate?" feeling. It seemed to culminate in his scream when Chamber exterminates the last, seemingly nice Hideauze later. Anyway, I'll have Xythar tend to this, if it needs fixing. ^_^}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Analysis of biological signatures complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All patterns match those of Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Organisms now designated as Hideauze larva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this their spawning ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceeding with the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to be this facility's administration block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that this is a type of recording medium used in extreme environments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you salvage the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Records successfully accessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Scanning for known data formats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Compatible format detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching inference engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting recovery and translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Recovery complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Display of data prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Prohibited?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This facility is confirmed to be a research institute of the ancient civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,However, further details are marked as classified by the Galactic Alliance of Humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Classified?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even relevant now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is military protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at our situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When unable to contact the main forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest-ranking officer present has authority to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And just who is the highest-ranking officer present here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Lieutenant Ledo, demand the display of the classified data
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from pilot support and development interface system Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Executing command.
Comment: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{the fun starts here}{1420}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to scout the place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Survey the area, and secure a foothold!{Raze, please check. Wanna make sure it's okay as imperative.}{yep. though i think that comma shouldn't be there}{They're independent clauses, so the comma is technically correct, but CMS says it can be removed for very short imperative compound sentences (e.g., "Run and eat"). Still, I was in doubt about what means "very short," so I kept the comma. :D}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,90,,Now is the time for mankind to walk using its own two feet.{1445}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,90,,And the volunteer who'll be taking the first step is our guest, Ryan Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,90,,This mission seems rather dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,90,,Well, nothing like this has ever been attempted before,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,90,,but I've got the best staff out there backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,90,,With their aid, this missi—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,90,,Now that the fifth ice age is closer than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,90,,our research is becoming more and more crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, many fear that such rapid scientific progress
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will destroy traditional values and will be detrimental to people's happiness and well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But religion and traditions have changed alongside the progress of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuous research may make happiness attainable for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby announce the birth of a stronghold of free science!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The advocates of augmented evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,commonly known as the Evolvers, are facing opposition all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's truly unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about your human genome experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which violate international regulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To overcome the crisis we are facing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it is necessary to be more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, current international regulations are outdat—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In response to the worsening global cooling,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there are calls to expedite the development of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Led by the Continental Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,space stations and interstellar migration vessels are being developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such space development is essential,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but that alone may not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it is not machines that will be going into space
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but we humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since last week's shocking leak of inside information,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the opposition against the Evolvers has been getting fiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Continental Union dispatched a multinational fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,without waiting for the UN's decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, there are also a number of countries siding with the Evolvers' cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is expected that the crisis will only worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Limited as we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,finding planets suitable for colonization
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,would take at least dozens of years, if not centuries.{"might" take? I'm not gonna mess with these last three lines, since vale double-checked them already...}{"would" is correct. it's sorta "considering our limitations, it would take us 9001 years to blah blah. original lines are fine and i wouldn't touch them =)}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There is but one solution to this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We must utilize and combine mechanical engineering and biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By evolving the human body itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we can adapt to the vacuum of space
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and to the astronomical distance and time requirements of interstellar travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The symbiont is a wonderful invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It can respire using the oxygen in seawater and endure the pressure of ocean depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll eventually adapt to the absolute-zero vacuum as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Symbiotic nanomachines provide their nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The method resembles photosynthesis but is far more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave good-bye to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Daddy going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week, the highly criticized Evolvers were under fire again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,due to a leak of their internal recruitment materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,which demonstrated that they had carried out atrocious human experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in violation of international law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With global cooling rapidly decreasing the area {in}habitable on Earth,{FYI: I chose this word order because "decreasing (an) area" almost always goes unbroken/together. And "decreasing the area [adjective]" isn't an unusual construct, as far as I know.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the conflict over the escape from the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,between the Continental Union and the Evolvers is intensifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, the frontlines are limited to outer space and to the launch sites on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but the hostilities are expected to increase in scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have discovered that the Continental Union is developing a large-scale wormhole drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The platforms are all equipped with self-destruct devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is clear that they intend to destroy the drive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,upon their escape of the Solar System, thus stranding us on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By attacking and taking control of the wormhole drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we Evolvers can extend our habitat to unknown galaxies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall conquer the infinity of space and achieve eternal prosperity!{Xythar: achieve/obtain/attain/reach prosperity, your choice. :)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That concludes the playable data.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple contradictions with information released by the Galactic Alliance exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Its credibility is extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what {\i1}was{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made it, and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is highly likely to be information manipulated by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy? What exactly {\i1}is{\i0} the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't the Hideauze supposed to be lower life forms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Surviving Hideauze identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all the equipment to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is Ledo doing?{"Ledo, what the hell are you doing?" seems like it'd fit audio well, even though I think it's not the TL.}{original is better imo}{Xythar, your choice. If you're indifferent, go with Raze's. :D}{yeah, i just think people don't normally address someone who's not even there directly in english. in fact, your suggestion is more in line with how the japanese commonly do it (not in this case though), but yeah not in english =S}{No way. I talk to imaginary non-present people all the time! >.>}{XD}
